---
title: Peppered Rib-Eye Steak with Truffled Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans Amandine
description: When you want to treat yourself to something luxuriantly tasty, nothing offers instant gratification better than a good steak. And we’ve got a great one with rib-eye, which is prized for its marbling and flavor. All it needs to be perfectly sublime is a simple pan sauce and some equally decadent sides, like almond green beans and truffled mashed potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peppered-rib-eye-steak-0a297c17.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/peppered-rib-eye-steak-b5431734.pdf
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/peppered-rib-eye-steak-59712984c9fd085960417ac2
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 750 kcal
  fat: 47 g
  saturated fat: 18 g
  carbohydrates: 52 g
  sugar: 11 g
